Hal Baylor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hal_Baylor 0 Hal Harvey Fieberling (born Hal David Britton on December 10, 1918 – January 15, 1998) known professionally as Hal Baylor, was an American actor, probably best known for his role as Pvt. 'Sky' Choynski in Sands of Iwo Jima.In addition to his acting career, he was also a boxer, with a record of 52-5 as an amateur and 16-8-3 as a professional.Baylor was born in San Antonio, Texas and died in Los Angeles.
